				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Hiya. I am a level 32 Warrior and went after Trazdon to get the Dark Circlet for the Crafted Greaves quest. He's located in the &quot;lava area&quot;, down by Bonecracker's room. It's tricky to find and get to, because coming from the Lavastorm ent, you make a left into one of the small room with meathooks in it. It looks like a small room, but if you keep going straight one of the walls is false and you go right through it. You then go down 2 sets of stairs, take the 2nd door from the right, then go through ANOTHER door, and that should be the room. There's a small lava pit in there with a couple mist elementals standing around. Sorry, that's the best directions to his room I can from memory. Someone else was kind enough to show it to me.<BR>
<BR>
So along the wall is a staircase going up. There are two spawn spots, typically held by magicians. One magician is at the first plateau of the stairs, the 2nd magician and the next plateau. If you continue going up the stairs, there's a door followed by a what looks to be a big drop. Didn't try it, so don't know where that leads. :) But the 2nd magician is the placeholder for Trazdon. Trazdon regularly appears every other time, so it goes magician, Trazdon, magician,....etc. Spawn is about every 20 minutes, so it takes 40 min. between Trazdon's. <BR>
<BR>
As a lvl 32 Warrior, I was able to control this room easily. The magicians were green and Trazdon was still blue to me. If you can, try and get the spawns of the 2 magicians apart, will make things easier when Trazdon appears. Trazdon's big trick is casting Fear. I have a magic resist of 46, and was able to resist all but twice. But he loves that spell and casts it a lot, so be prepared.<BR>
<BR>
I got the circlet on the 2nd kill for him. Didn't take it any further than that, so don't know how lucky I may have been. Off to S. Karana now to get my greaves. Hope this info helps!<BR>
<BR>
Toreck, Level 32 Troll Warrior 
